<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-21-0364 </DOCNO><TEXT>This article presents work on Kripkean analysis of intuitionistic modallogic. One possible explanation for so little literature on this subjectis simply that it is hardly obvious what the applications would be. Itseems to the authors however that there is a wide range of computationalapplications and indeed so many are the possibilities that it is worthbeginning by sorting out the basic theory.</TEXT></DOC>